    <item>
      <title>英国各党派联合敦促特朗普反思马斯克的干预行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/uk-parties-unite-in-urging-trump-to-rethink-musk-s-meddling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前，亿万富翁特斯拉老板唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 就英国政治发表了一系列愈发煽动性的言论，包括支持极右翼人物。英国三大政党的资深政治家私下敦促唐纳德·特朗普的盟友重新考虑他与埃隆·马斯克的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/uk-parties-unite-in-urging-trump-to-rethink-musk-s-meddling</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 15:36:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克为何涉足英国儿童性侵团伙丑闻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/why-is-elon-musk-criticizing-keir-starmer-over-uk-grooming-gang-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克指责英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 参与了数十年前发生的儿童性剥削团伙丑闻，此举让英国政府陷入守势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/why-is-elon-musk-criticizing-keir-starmer-over-uk-grooming-gang-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 15:11:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求上诉法院暂停纽约判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/trump-asks-new-york-appeals-court-to-stop-hush-money-sentencing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普请求纽约一名法官推迟原定于 1 月 10 日作出的封口费判决，以便这位当选总统可以在就职典礼前对此案的有罪判决提出质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/trump-asks-new-york-appeals-court-to-stop-hush-money-sentencing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 14:37:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
